docs.abstract: French officials investigate armed robbery of reality television star Kim Kardashian, who was allegedly tied up, gagged and robbed of jewelry worth almost $9 million in luxurious apartment in Eighth Arrondissement of Paris; highly publicized theft during Parish Fashion Week has negatively impacted tourism in France, which has already suffered following two major terrorist attacks since 2015.
